# ffuf-intel

Python 3 CLI that wraps **[ffuf](https://github.com/ffuf/ffuf)** with **auto-calibration**, **async deep content inspection**, and **behavioral next-hop fuzzing**.

Use only on systems you are authorized to test.

## Setup

```bash
cd C:\Users\UsamaHafeez\Downloads\ffuf_intel
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e .
```

## Usage

```bash
ffuf-intel -u https://target.example/FUZZ -w C:\path\to\wordlist.txt
```

See full docs in the project README sections for options, triggers, and legal notice.
